Title: Merlin interlocking system
Description: Designed specifically for use in commercial kitchens, this Merlin CT1200S gas ventilation interlock system is used where kitchen appliances have flame failure devices and gas proving is not a requirement. Acting as an interlock between the ventilation system and the gas solenoid valve, this system can work with external current monitors and air pressure differential switches for interlocking with up to two fans.

Title: Clesse Clessinox hose assembly swiwel female 3/4'' x 22mm 70kW Stainless Steel
Description: This Clesse Clessinox 1.2M stainless steel metallic flexible hose assembly with 3/4" swivel female and male x male adapter x 22mm compression fitting is suitable for use in final stage installations where a 3/4" outlet on the regulator and fixed flexible pipe is needed. Rodent-resistant and with a certified 1MB pressure loss per metre at 70kW/h, this hose assembly can also be used in meter boxes up to 70kW/h.
